# Copyrighted book illustrations — never committed. Referenced by packs as `stonetop-art/...`
# (resolves to Foundry's Data/stonetop-art/). Regenerate from a book you own with
# `npm run extract-art`; see stonetop-art/README.md (the only tracked file here).
/stonetop-art/*
!/stonetop-art/README.md

# Raw mutool stext dumps — large; compact *.lines.json fixtures are committed instead
tests/import/pdf/fixtures/*.stext.xml
